* Biomass watched Perndabot very carefully, seeing his muscles strain to get 
ready for the strike. His own muscles bunched under strain as he readied 
himself for impact and a strike if his own when, just then, another male bot 
made the sceen.
He looked over towards FZ as he entered the area, not even noticing 
Perndabot stand down and Nue'e nearly jump out of her armor. In fact, the 
startled femm stumbled back and tripped over the large gustalt's foot, 
lanting on it with a thud.
Biomass lifted a brow and watched FZ, who was this man anyway. He must be 
some sort of higher authority to command Perndabot like that.
Was he the commander?
But Nue'e was the first to answer FZs question before any others.*

" A bunch of showing off."

* She got to her feet, though still standing on the foot. She moved her 
glasses back up her face and looked at FZ. But then it was her turn to lift 
a brow when amother femal came, some cat-bot (feline). She rolled her optics 
at the way that she stood and talked, shaking her head and wondering if all 
the women on this planet acted like this and how it would be a shame if they 
did.
Biomass, on the other hand, hoped that ALL women were like this one when he 
saw her. His eyes couldn't help but move down her body but what interest he 
had he hid and then turned to look back at FZ.
But soon the woman had gone to do FZs bidding and that left them as they 
were before, waiting for FZ to speak or something to happen.*
